# Designs

---

## Provider-D1 多提供商 AI 调度
**Status:** draft

**状态：** 草案
**模块：** `backend/src/ai.rs`
**标签：** stack:backend
**依赖：** ApiSources-G1, ApiSources-D1

```rust
/// 将流式聊天请求调度到正确的提供商。
/// 失败时返回错误消息，成功时返回 None。
pub async fn dispatch_chat(
    source: &ApiSource,
    model: &str,
    system: &str,
    messages: Vec<ChatMessage>,
    tx: UnboundedSender<AIStreamDelta>,
) -> Option<String>

/// 构建提供商专属的请求 URL。
fn build_api_url(source: &ApiSource) -> String

/// 构建提供商专属的认证请求头。
fn build_auth_headers(source: &ApiSource) -> HeaderMap

/// 将提供商专属的 SSE 流解析为文本增量。
fn parse_sse_delta(provider: &Provider, data: &str) -> Option<String>
```

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Routing: dispatch_chat()
    Routing --> AnthropicStream: provider == Anthropic
    Routing --> OpenAIStream: provider == OpenAI
    Routing --> LocalStream: provider == Local
    AnthropicStream --> Emitting: SSE content_block_delta
    OpenAIStream --> Emitting: SSE choices[0].delta.content
    LocalStream --> Emitting: Ollama /api/chat response
    Emitting --> Emitting: more deltas
    Emitting --> Done: stream ends
    Emitting --> Error: connection/API error
    Done --> [*]
    Error --> [*]
```

| 提供商 | 认证请求头 | API 路径 | SSE 格式 |
|---|---|---|---|
| Anthropic | `x-api-key: {key}` | `/v1/messages` | `event: content_block_delta` → `delta.text` |
| OpenAI | `Authorization: Bearer {key}` | `/v1/chat/completions` | `choices[0].delta.content` |
| Local | 无（或 Bearer） | `/v1/chat/completions` | 与 OpenAI 相同（Ollama 兼容） |

```
fn dispatch_chat(source, model, system, messages, tx):
    url = build_api_url(source)
    headers = build_auth_headers(source)
    body = build_request_body(source.provider, model, system, messages)

    resp = http_post(url, headers, body, stream=true)
    if not resp.ok:
        return Some(format("API error ({})", resp.status))

    for chunk in resp.bytes_stream():
        for sse_event in parse_sse(chunk):
            text = parse_sse_delta(source.provider, sse_event.data)
            if text:
                tx.send(AIStreamDelta { text })

    return None  // success

fn build_api_url(source):
    match source.provider:
        Anthropic => "{base}/v1/messages"
        OpenAI => "{base}/v1/chat/completions"
        Local => "{source.url}/v1/chat/completions"

fn parse_sse_delta(provider, data):
    json = parse(data)
    match provider:
        Anthropic => json.delta.text  (from content_block_delta)
        OpenAI => json.choices[0].delta.content
        Local => json.choices[0].delta.content  // Ollama compatible
```

- `ClaudeProvider::chat_stream()` 重构为 `dispatch_chat()`
- `forge/ai.rs` 中的 `ToolClaudeProvider` 泛化为使用 `dispatch_chat()` 配合 `ApiSource`
- 保留现有的 `ModelConfig::cheap()/standard()/strong()` 作为降级默认配置
- `ai.rs` 中的 `load_api_config()` 替换为 `config::resolve_api_key()`

